# 360Ghar Backend Project Structure

## Main Entry Points
- **Application Entry**: [app/main.py](mdc:app/main.py) - FastAPI application initialization
- **Alternative Runner**: [run.py](mdc:run.py) - Alternative application runner

## Core Application Structure

### API Layer
- **API Router**: [app/api/api_v1/api.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/api.py) - Main API router configuration
- **Endpoints**:
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/auth.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/auth.py) - Supabase authentication endpoints
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/users.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/users.py) - User management and profiles
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/properties.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/properties.py) - Property CRUD and search
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/agents.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/agents.py) - Agent management and assignment
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/bookings.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/bookings.py) - Short-stay booking system
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/visits.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/visits.py) - Property visit scheduling
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/swipes.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/swipes.py) - Tinder-like swipe interactions
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/amenities.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/amenities.py) - Property amenities management
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/upload.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/upload.py) - File upload handling
  - [app/api/api_v1/endpoints/core.py](mdc:app/api/api_v1/endpoints/core.py) - System management (bugs, pages, FAQs, versions)

### Business Logic Layer
- **Services**: Located in [app/services/](mdc:app/services/) - Async business logic implementations
  - [app/services/user.py](mdc:app/services/user.py) - User management and Supabase integration
  - [app/services/property.py](mdc:app/services/property.py) - Property CRUD and search with PostGIS
  - [app/services/agent.py](mdc:app/services/agent.py) - Agent assignment and management
  - [app/services/booking.py](mdc:app/services/booking.py) - Short-stay booking logic
  - [app/services/visit.py](mdc:app/services/visit.py) - Visit scheduling and management
  - [app/services/swipe.py](mdc:app/services/swipe.py) - Swipe matching and recommendations
  - [app/services/core.py](mdc:app/services/core.py) - Core system services
  - [app/services/storage.py](mdc:app/services/storage.py) - Supabase storage integration

### Data Layer
- **Models**: Split into separate files in [app/models/](mdc:app/models/) for better organization
  - [app/models/users.py](mdc:app/models/users.py) - User, UserSwipe, UserSearchHistory models
  - [app/models/properties.py](mdc:app/models/properties.py) - Property, PropertyImage, Amenity, PropertyAmenity, Visit models
  - [app/models/agents.py](mdc:app/models/agents.py) - Agent model
  - [app/models/bookings.py](mdc:app/models/bookings.py) - Booking model
  - [app/models/core.py](mdc:app/models/core.py) - System models (BugReport, Page, FAQ, AppVersion)
  - [app/models/enums.py](mdc:app/models/enums.py) - All enumeration definitions
- **Database Configuration**: [app/core/database.py](mdc:app/core/database.py) - Async SQLAlchemy with PostgreSQL
- **Types**: [app/db/types.py](mdc:app/db/types.py) - Database type definitions

### Schema Layer
- **Pydantic Schemas**: Located in [app/schemas/](mdc:app/schemas/) - Request/response validation
  - [app/schemas/user.py](mdc:app/schemas/user.py) - User-related schemas with validation
  - [app/schemas/property.py](mdc:app/schemas/property.py) - Property schemas with unified filtering
  - [app/schemas/agent.py](mdc:app/schemas/agent.py) - Agent management schemas
  - [app/schemas/booking.py](mdc:app/schemas/booking.py) - Booking system schemas
  - [app/schemas/visit.py](mdc:app/schemas/visit.py) - Visit scheduling schemas
  - [app/schemas/amenity.py](mdc:app/schemas/amenity.py) - Amenity schemas
  - [app/schemas/core.py](mdc:app/schemas/core.py) - System schemas (bugs, pages, FAQs)
  - [app/schemas/common.py](mdc:app/schemas/common.py) - Shared schemas and utilities

### Configuration and Core Systems
- **Configuration**: [app/core/config.py](mdc:app/core/config.py) - Pydantic settings with environment variables
- **Authentication**: [app/core/auth.py](mdc:app/core/auth.py) - Supabase authentication integration
- **Database**: [app/core/database.py](mdc:app/core/database.py) - Async SQLAlchemy with PostgreSQL
- **Caching**: [app/core/cache.py](mdc:app/core/cache.py) - Redis caching (optional)
- **Logging**: [app/core/logging.py](mdc:app/core/logging.py) - Structured logging with JSON format
- **Exceptions**: [app/core/exceptions.py](mdc:app/core/exceptions.py) - Custom exception classes with error codes

### Utilities
- **Validators**: [app/utils/validators.py](mdc:app/utils/validators.py) - Phone number and data validation utilities
- **Distance**: [app/utils/distance.py](mdc:app/utils/distance.py) - Geographic distance calculations

### Middleware
- **Rate Limiting**: [app/middleware/rate_limit.py](mdc:app/middleware/rate_limit.py) - Request rate limiting
- **Security**: [app/middleware/security.py](mdc:app/middleware/security.py) - Security headers and CORS

## Infrastructure and Deployment
- **Docker**: [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile) and [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml)
- **Deployment**: [railway.toml](mdc:railway.toml) and [Procfile](mdc:Procfile)
- **Database Migrations**: [supabase/migrations/](mdc:supabase/migrations/)

## Testing
- **Test Files**: [tests/](mdc:tests/)
- **Data Population**: [populate_data/](mdc:populate_data/) - Test data generation scripts

